snippet.title: NHL 14 Official E3 2013 Trailer
snippet.description: NHL 14 Official E3 2013 Trailer. NHL 14 will feature Big Hits. Real Fights. Unbelievable Speed and Skill. This is the trailer playing on the E3 show floor, straight to your screen. NHL 14 will release September 10, 2013 in North America and by September 13, 2013 Worldwide on the PS3 and X360. Preview all the new NHL 14 features' and pre-order now at http://bit.ly/135ZWA2
